column1: PLEASE READ: If you intend to use these data in a publication, we request that you:
Acknowledge use of the ATNF Pulsar Catalogue, both by giving the Catalogue web address and by referencing the paper: Manchester, R. N., Hobbs, G.B., Teoh, A. & Hobbs, M., AJ, 129, 1993-2006 (2005)
